which we just looked at,

00:13:48.234 --> 00:13:50.567
and other accessibility
standards.

00:13:50.567 --> 00:13:53.934
And it helps me work with
dynamic web applications

00:13:53.934 --> 00:13:55.701
that we're now seeing,
uh,

00:13:55.701 --> 00:13:58.133
by giving me,
uh, dynamic updates.

00:13:58.133 --> 00:14:02.000
It tells me when things change
on the web page.

00:14:02.000 --> 00:14:06.501
So there are some cases where
I want information spoken to me

00:14:06.501 --> 00:14:08.834
and there are some cases
where I don't want,

00:14:08.834 --> 00:14:11.467
uh, kind of the intrusive voice
to come up,

00:14:11.467 --> 00:14:13.234
but I want maybe just some
audio indicator.

00:14:13.234 --> 00:14:15.000
